{"tid":786732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日男籃4成員穿隊服印尼尋歡遭遣返","createTime":"2018-08-20T06:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T09:39:09.000Z","uid":71708,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"131f88bcfa4d5582a1a760f17316836d7cd80088","tid":786732,"uid":71708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"日本國家男籃昨夜被爆出有4名成員，身穿國家隊制服深夜在雅加達紅燈區尋歡作樂。<br />\n<br />\n日本代表團團長山下泰裕今天上午召開記者會致歉，4名違規成員被即時開除並將遣返回國。<br />\n<br />\n據《朝日新聞》報道，日本國家男籃在上周四(16日)晚對卡塔爾之戰結束後，包括23歲的橋本拓哉、22歲的今村佳太、23歲的佐藤卓磨以及27歲永吉佑也等4名成員，在深夜穿上球隊制服到當地紅燈區尋歡，甚至帶女服務生外出。<br />\n<br />\n日本男籃在開除4人後，餘下比賽將會只剩8名球員應戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1921475/%E6%97%A5%E7%94%B7%E7%B1%834%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E7%A9%BF%E9%9A%8A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%B0%8B%E6%AD%A1%E9%81%AD%E9%81%A3%E8%BF%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1921475%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25B1%25834%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E5%25B0%258B%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%2581%25A3%25E8%25BF%2594&d=ijgpc%2BAPKghHsf2yIHXsNDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=b81757e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1921475/%E6%97%A5%E7%94%B7%E7%B1%834%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E7%A9%BF%E9%9A%8A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%B0%8B%E6%AD%A1%E9%81%AD%E9%81%A3%E8%BF%94</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即刻炒晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52f589f7796186ac0ca06d79393840ded2500db","tid":786732,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:58:33.000Z","msg":"印尼妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=